{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 HPRSSN Hidden VKB\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 A REAPER extension that turns your computer keyboard into a MIDI keyboard \u8212? like the built-in VKB, but without the window.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs28 Features\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Two keyboard layouts: REAPER (default) and Ableton\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Octave/velocity overlay anchored to the REAPER window\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Exclusive Arm \u8212? arming a track disarms the rest\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Exclusive Solo \u8212? soloing a track unsolos the rest\sa180\par}
}
